ast_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "hash": "b151c31cdce31991a550d942e48e8ea5b48019f2c93c11dd2479f507c8932177", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "4c20ba87-4d8d-4d8b-ac75-76a14a533e84", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "733f70702d1bbc1f9894d2932a26209f7649f3cfb5d3ef89f9128fa8fd33b156", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "COCO\u2029INFO\u2010SHEET\nCOCo \u2013 The Centre for Community Organizations3680 Jeanne-Mance, #470 Montreal (QC) H2X 2K5 ph: (514) 849-5599 or (866) 552-2626 fax: (514) 849-5553 or (866) 560-2626info@coco-net.org | www.coco-net.org\n\u2029Key\u2029Ques2ons\u2029to\u2029Consider\u2029When\u2029Thinking\u2029About\u2029Con\ufb02ictsof\u2029InterestWhat\u2029is\u2029a\u2029\u201ccon\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u201d?A\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029occurs\u2029when\u2029someone\u2029in\u2029a\u2029posi3on\u2029of\u2029trust\u2029has\u2029compe3ng\u2029professional\u2029orpersonal\u2029interests.\u2029These\u2029compe3ng\u2029interests\u2029can\u2029possibly\u2029interfere\u2029with\u2029the\u2029person\u2019s\u2029ability\u2029to\u2029remainimpar3al\u2029as\u2029they\u2029ful\ufb01ll\u2029their\u2029du3es.\u2029A\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029involves\u2029not\u2029just\u2029the\u2029issue\u2029in\u2029ques3on,\u2029butalso\u2029people's\u2029percep3on\u2029of\u2029the\u2029issue\u2029and\u2029who\u2029is\u2029involved\u2029in\u2029making\u2029a\u2029decision.\u2029A\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interestexists\u2029even\u2029if\u2029no\u2029unethical\u2029or\u2029inappropriate\u2029decisions\u2029are\u2029made.\u2029A\u2029key\u2029element\u2029of\u2029being\u2029a\u2029board\u2029member\u2029is\u2029ac3ng\u2029with\u2029honesty\u2029and\u2029loyalty\u2029towards\u2029the\u2029organiza3on.This\u2029means\u2029that\u2029board\u2029members\u2029are\u2029expected\u2029to\u2029avoid\u2029con\ufb02icts\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029and\u2029to\u2029disclose\u2029them\u2029ifthey\u2029exist.\u2029Board\u2029members\u2029are\u2029always\u2029required\u2029to\u2029act\u2029in\u2029the\u2029best\u2029interests\u2029of\u2029the\u2029organiza3on.\u2029\u2029Dealing\u2029with\u2029con\ufb02icts\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029can\u2029be\u2029tricky!\u2029Healthy\u2029prac3ces\u2029include\u2029having\u2029a\u2029democra3cally\u2010runorganiza3on\u2029where\u2029people\u2029from\u2029the\u2029community\u2029are\u2029involved\u2029at\u2029all\u2029levels\u2029(including\u2029the\u2029board).\u2029Thismeans\u2029that\u2029the\u2029roles\u2029people\u2029play\u2029in\u2029the\u2029organiza3on\u2029oLen\u2029overlap.\u2029But\u2029just\u2029because\u2029con\ufb02icts\u2029ofinterest\u2029can\u2029be\u2029challenging\u2029doesn't\u2029mean\u2029you\u2029can't\u2029par3cipate\u2029in\u2029the\u2029organiza3ons\u2029you\u2029care\u2029about.\u2029What\u2029a\u2029board\u2029member\u2029decides\u2029to\u2029do\u2029about\u2029a\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029is\u2029an\u2029individual\u2029choice.\u2029This\u2029meansthey\u2029have\u2029to\u2029decide\u2029whether\u2029to\u2029abstain\u2029from\u2029making\u2029a\u2029decision\u2029if\u2029they\u2029are\u2029involved\u2029or\u2029appear\u2029to\u2029beinvolved\u2029in\u2029a\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1684, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "4c20ba87-4d8d-4d8b-ac75-76a14a533e84": {"__data__": {"id_": "4c20ba87-4d8d-4d8b-ac75-76a14a533e84", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "0b5b5a27-bd9d-48b5-a1f0-714eb1c35202", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "hash": "b151c31cdce31991a550d942e48e8ea5b48019f2c93c11dd2479f507c8932177", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "d30d535c-affb-4579-983b-369b2958a3fd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "hash": "7f76f66dc3ec947011df204615a6c306a2f7c30bace303b269d0e9acc90cf423", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "For\u2029board\u2029members,\u2029no\u2029one\u2029else\u2029can\u2029decide\u2029that\u2029someone\u2029can'tpar3cipate\u2029in\u2029a\u2029discussion\u2029or\u2029can't\u2029vote\u2029on\u2029a\u2029given\u2029issue\u2029due\u2029to\u2029a\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest.\u2029It\u2029is\u2029up\u2029to\u2029theperson\u2029involved\u2029in\u2029the\u2029actual\u2029or\u2029perceived\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029to\u2029make\u2029that\u2029decision.\u2029However,\u2029if\u2029aboard\u2029member\u2029is\u2029in\u2029a\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029and\u2029doesn't\u2029abstain,\u2029that\u2029decision\u2029may\u2029be\u2029challenged.\u2029By\u2010lawscan\u2029serve\u2029as\u2029a\u2029good\u2029guide\u2029on\u2029how\u2029con\ufb02icts\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029are\u2029handled\u2029within\u2029our\u2029organiza3ons.\u2029However,by\u2010laws\u2029can\u2029never\u2029force\u2029a\u2029board\u2029members\u2029to\u2029not\u2029par3cipate\u2029in\u2029discussing\u2029an\u2029issue\u2029or\u2029making\u2029adecision.\u2029Building\u2029a\u2029culture\u2029where\u2029dialogue\u2029and\u2029transparency\u2029are\u2029valued\u2029is\u2029an\u2029important\u2029means\u2029ofencouraging\u2029people\u2029to\u2029talk\u2029about\u2029con\ufb02icts\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029when\u2029they\u2029arise.PUBLISHED\u2029NOVEMBER\u20292010Because\u2029we\u2029are\u2029not\u2029lawyers\u2029at\u2029COCo,\u2029our\u2029info\u2010sheets\u2029only\u2029present\u2029general\u2029informa9on.\u2029COCo\u2029never\u2029provides\u2029legal\u2029advice.\u2029While\u2029we\u2029do\u2029our\u2029best\u2029to\u2029ensurethat\u2029our\u2029informa9on\u2029is\u2029accurate,\u2029please\u2029consult\u2029a\u2029lawyer\u2029if\u2029you\u2029want\u2029professional\u2029assurance\u2029that\u2029our\u2029informa9on,\u2029and\u2029your\u2029interpreta9on\u2029of\u2029it,\u2029isappropriate\u2029to\u2029your\u2029par9cular\u2029situa9on.\u2029You\u2029can\u2029contact\u2029COCo\u2029for\u2029a\u2029list\u2029of\u2029lawyers\u2029with\u2029experience\u2029working\u2029with\u2029community\u2029groups.\u2029\u2029Please\u2029know\u2029thatCOCo\u2029cannot\u2029take\u2029responsibility\u2029for\u2029your\u2029use\u2029and\u2029interpreta9on\u2029of\u2029the\u2029informa9on\u2029in\u2029our\u2029info\u2010sheets.1", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1685, "end_char_idx": 2971, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e4b45e87-f8d8-43d8-bb09-784f7ea602f9": {"__data__": {"id_": "e4b45e87-f8d8-43d8-bb09-784f7ea602f9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "2", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "faee0b96-0131-450c-a006-fbf1df04a52f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"page_label": "2", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "hash": "2a80da7621a22ca8f2d77399fc67d5c4a8a394bcca9be47303531384ec363c3d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "7948a162-0040-424c-961a-250c1d7c1cd1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "28bba2d0fdd0bcbdd2a8f62a3aa20cacfc051723ccf45a97dfd93a08d1820b32", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "COCO\u2029INFO\u2010SHEET\nCOCo \u2013 The Centre for Community Organizations3680 Jeanne-Mance, #470 Montreal (QC) H2X 2K5 ph: (514) 849-5599 or (866) 552-2626 fax: (514) 849-5553 or (866) 560-2626info@coco-net.org | www.coco-net.orgSample\u2029\u201ccon\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u201d\u2029by\u2010law:A\u2029director\u2029must\u2029report\u2029any\u2029situa3on\u2029of\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029of\u2029interest\u2029he\u2029is\u2029facing\u2029to\u2029the\u2029board\u2029of\u2029directors\u2029andsuch\u2029con\ufb02ict\u2029must\u2029be\u2029noted\u2029in\u2029the\u2029minutes\u2029of\u2029the\u2029mee3ng\u2029following\u2029the\u2029disclosure.\u2029\u2029The\u2029member\u2029shallabstain\u2029from\u2029par3cipa3ng\u2029except\u2029to\u2029answers\u2029ques3ons\u2029from\u2029board\u2029members\u2029in\u2029any\u2029discussion\u2029andvote\u2029on\u2029the\u2029issueShould\u2029board\u2029members\u2029get\u2029paid?\u2029While\u2029board\u2029members\u2029are\u2029legally\u2029allowed\u2029to\u2029be\u2029paid\u2029for\u2029their\u2029services\u2029as\u2029board\u2029members,\u2029in\u2029prac3cesthis\u2029is\u2029not\u2029well\u2029looked\u2029upon\u2029by\u2029the\u2029community\u2029or\u2029funders.\u2029Many\u2029organiza3ons\u2029may\u2029choose\u2029to\u2029have\u2029anexplicit\u2029by\u2010law\u2029that\u2029clearly\u2029states\u2029that\u2029board\u2029members\u2029should\u2029not\u2029be\u2029paid\u2029for\u2029siQng\u2029on\u2029the\u2029board.Board\u2029members\u2029are\u2029allowed\u2029to\u2029enter\u2029into\u2029contracts\u2029to\u2029do\u2029di\ufb00erent\u2029kinds\u2029of\u2029work\u2029for\u2029the\u2029organiza3on.However,\u2029this\u2029must\u2029be\u2029made\u2029public\u2029to\u2029all\u2029board\u2029members;\u2029recorded\u2029in\u2029the\u2029mee3ng\u2029minutes;\u2029andapproved\u2029by\u2029the\u2029Board.\u2029In\u2029this\u2029case,\u2029it\u2029is\u2029a\u2029healthy\u2029prac3ce\u2029for\u2029the\u2029Board\u2029member\u2029in\u2029ques3on\u2029toabstain\u2029from\u2029the\u2029discussion\u2029and\u2029vo3ng.\u2029There\u2029are\u2029pros\u2029and\u2029cons\u2029to\u2029contrac3ng\u2029with\u2029board\u2029members.\u2029On\u2029one\u2029hand,\u2029this\u2029allows\u2029an\u2029organiza3onto\u2029get\u2029greatly\u2029discounted\u2029professional\u2029services\u2029(for\u2029example\u2029graphic\u2029design).\u2029On\u2029the\u2029other\u2029hand,\u2029it\u2029canbe\u2029messy.\u2029Honesty,\u2029transparency\u2029and\u2029keeping\u2029\u2029good\u2029records\u2029of\u2029the\u2029decisions\u2029we\u2029make\u2029are\u2029key.\u2029It\u2029is\u2029agood\u2029idea\u2029for\u2029contracts\u2029with\u2029board\u2029members\u2029to\u2029be\u2029in\u2029wri3ng.\u2029\u2029\u2029Sample\u2029by\u2010law\u2029on\u2029board\u2029remuneraEon:\u2029Directors\u2029are\u2029not\u2029remunerated\u2029for\u2029holding\u2029o\ufb03ce.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1654, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7948a162-0040-424c-961a-250c1d7c1cd1": {"__data__": {"id_": "7948a162-0040-424c-961a-250c1d7c1cd1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "2", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "faee0b96-0131-450c-a006-fbf1df04a52f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"page_label": "2", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "hash": "2a80da7621a22ca8f2d77399fc67d5c4a8a394bcca9be47303531384ec363c3d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "e4b45e87-f8d8-43d8-bb09-784f7ea602f9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"page_label": "2", "file_name": "conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_path": "data\\prod\\docs\\conflict-of-interest-final-nov-2010.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 180754, "creation_date": "2025-01-27", "last_modified_date": "2025-01-27"}, "hash": "62c044f773de5f2b84dcd3a47d7fe15723c44a3f591a4f530330413eed2cff29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metada